Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  会长就没有不困的早上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡了几个小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jennifer一直都是这么说的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「睡眠不足可是美容的大敌」哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  挚爱的Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那如丝般润滑的肌肤  I wanna touch you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明爱理他们马上就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有大人物要来视察嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  诗织阿姨  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这是要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  休息日加班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  你就是KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who is it？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗织阿姨  佳织的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really！？  不是sister吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  爱理  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  难得来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们慢慢玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  都买来了哦  牛奶和鸡蛋还有黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这些就行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  别的都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是文化节上用的点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什么点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为必须提前一天先做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能做些简单的烤制点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要做  就认真尝试看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭是佳织亲手做的这一点  粉丝们肯定会络绎不绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角不是天象仪吗  咖啡厅只是顺带的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两边都是主角啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出来的点心也是越好吃越好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你会做点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好失礼啊  别看我这样手还是很灵巧的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没有做过而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听着佳织的指示啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥意思啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是佳织  你手腕的伤没问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是像平常一样用的话没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了  结说一会她也会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川要来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过凪沙学姐好像有事来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要变热闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结知道来我家的路么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且把地图发给凪沙学姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西有必要非得自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天象仪什么的  店里买个不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  这样说的话点心也可以去店里买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不就没有存在的价值了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  累死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干了连半小时都没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不擅长这种平凡的活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  反正开始就没指望过你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Treasure…get！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:05:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的嘛  My friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最先做的已经烤好啦  想让你们尝一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸展运动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Stretch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Scone！这玩意看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好试验品一号刚烤好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结也来尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去倒点红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是走着来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  因为天气非常好顺便能光合作用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说是日光浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜  要是凪沙学姐也在的话全员就能凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙学姐好像过一会也能来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  谁让你随便开始吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  不是要试吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只是偷吃而已吧  不给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦  还有好多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织是Angel啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Demon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  KENNY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我  做的真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正大部分都是佳织做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也撒了粉  做了形状的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这个能成为天文学会的招牌商品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  先定下来把这个加入菜单  接下来还要再加几个别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来想试着做下曲奇饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结能来一起帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结会烧饭做菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要这样来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要用那个来开星座的小洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  用微妙的大小区别来调整通光量从而再现星空的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心谨慎才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概要开多少个洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少个呢  肉眼能看到的星星大概有数千个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesus  好蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤好要多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三四分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会能借用一些时间吗  有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么  在我面前不能说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等那边烤好了再说行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  那就一会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟  这个模特的腰部曲线和Jennifer一模一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了  尾宿八做的太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就行了嘛  那种东西没人会在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！说不定就会有对观星非常感兴趣的人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有更好用的工具就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颜色也想好好再现一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}嗯  Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  烤的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,样子就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  毕竟第一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊  是不是去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后一定会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  结  曲奇烤好了哦  来尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  结也说好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  我也再来一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  成功了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦  这边只能我自己做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试验品二号做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈  等死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像形状各异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是试验品了啊  快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天应该能做的差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不要踩那里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一如既往乏味的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也尝尝味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木同学喜欢秋山同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为  为什么突然问这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果未来  这样的生活如此持续下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不知道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和奏只不过是普通的青梅竹马而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结  难道你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动室里的红茶差不多要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该补充一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都能记着真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  爱理回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏说要出去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去买东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要买些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以干脆就出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想尝试更多种类的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要去买点材料回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要什么只要说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会帮你们买回来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去买也很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就去地下的食品区了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是要买杂货  大概是在上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KENNY能来这边帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还提不了重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要买什么啊  准备买那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是很多东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结就过去帮一下奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要好好盯着奏不要浪费钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  佐佐木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了我刚才说的要买红茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把他们两个凑到一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  没什么原因的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是活动室里常喝的那个你精挑细选的红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  马上就要喝完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是结告诉我  到时候还得特地再过来买
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这些就齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  和佳织的挺像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  让你陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到什么有意思的东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  这个看起来好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我一口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No money
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给我忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的分你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}噢  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Thanks so  so very very very much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在一起真的很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个磅蛋糕怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sounds good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责的已经做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就到这里负责试吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是有多饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫我还处在身体疯长的阶段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去帮秋山同学的忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算去了也没什么事干的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那结你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  看上去不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来看看能不能帮你点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山同学你真的很喜欢星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只记得小时候看到的星空漂亮得令我感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在地面上看见的星辰的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前发出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从遥远的宇宙历经漫长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才终于抵达这里的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处女座银河距离地球是239万光年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所见到的光是239万年前的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,239万年  无论是时间上还是距离上都让人难以想象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个从后面照一下试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还没有加上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是夏季的星座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后你想起些什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要着急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候总会想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得某个人的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张侧脸虽然在微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却又非常的忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是古川的亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是亲人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太清楚  不过对古川来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是个和你有很深的关联的人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为刚才古川说话的时候显得很悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那个人对我来说应该是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  一二三等星都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  我是结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡傻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之临时组装完之后去看看那边的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  佳织来过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在说这句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底选哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like them all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是会很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  你觉得天象仪真的能吸引来顾客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底  大家期待的只是佳织的女仆装和亲手做的点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得天文学会的会长说这个是不是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.81,0:19:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  KENNY偶尔也会说些正经话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管哪个看上去都很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我姑且也帮了忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,华宫学姐也试吃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉  什么都没能帮到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么  这话凪沙一说听上去好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是来接结的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是试装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过天象仪也已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  关灯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fantastic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是奏做出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  底座是KENNY做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面的部分结也来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然用名字称呼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  没什么大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  比起这个  还是快看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  那就是夏季大三角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来天文宅发挥本领了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.51,0:20:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大三角的织女星虽然看上去是白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在夏季南边天空上天蝎座的心宿二却被称为红超巨星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发着红色的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说为什么会有颜色的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为表面温度的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心宿二大约在3500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色的织女星大约是9500度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提  太阳的表面温度大约是6000度左右
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天  谢谢你来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只做到三等星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但至少在文化节之前能完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过嘛  接下来才是重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更小的四五等星的洞差不多要钻3000个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等级是依靠光亮来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际的亮度和观测时的亮度还是有区别的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫绝对星等和视星等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个天象仪总之…
